{"tid":1460500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大總理：香港政府要聆聽市民的擔憂","createTime":"2019-08-13T03:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:10:49.000Z","uid":134071,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1f538a5c89bc4168a86b61ef5f17c222d83ffaa3","tid":1460500,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:15:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2882498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2882498&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9yq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=d5847ab3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2882498&h=aa0a9580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2882498</a><br />\n<br />\n譴責暴力 杜魯道、美參院多數黨領袖對香港事件發聲<br />\n2019-08-13 08:52<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港「反送中」警民衝突愈演愈烈，西方國家也對此表達關注，加拿大總理杜魯道呼籲北京當局，對待港人憂慮要謹慎且尊重，美國參議院多數黨領袖麥康奈爾（Mitch McConnell）也譴責暴力鎮壓「不能接受」。<br />\n<br />\n《CBC》報導，加拿大總理杜魯道週一表示，由於有許多加拿大公民居住香港，他非常擔心香港近來的狀況，並呼籲香港政府要聆聽市民的擔憂，北京當局要謹慎且尊重，他也強調加拿大期盼和平、秩序與對話。報導指出，約有30萬的加拿大公民住在香港。<br />\n<br />\n美國參議院多數黨領袖麥康奈爾（Mitch McConnell）12日在推特表示，當北京試圖侵犯他們的自治與自由時，香港人勇敢地對抗中國共產黨，任何暴力鎮壓都是不能接受的，全世界都在關注。"},{"pid":"6286e1327e9d7a7e354c248443c408448fb49351","tid":1460500,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445355c198f6450d5c55d835a4c4ce7716c4f65d","tid":1460500,"uid":246118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:16:51.000Z","msg":"（緊急）（無人講？）有無人知超過30個鐘 811被捕人士新屋嶺見到律師未<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460350</a><br />\